               <lb n="003"/> As <name type= "person"> John <seg> <note target="n4">4</note> </seg></name> 
                         is going home I take 
                        <lb n="004"/> the opportunity of dropping you a few lines
                        <lb n="005"/> to inform you that I am well.  We arrived here
                        <lb n="006"/> at noon today we have had bad luck since
                        <lb n="007"/> I wrote you last. We broke our shaft on our up 
                        <lb n="008"/> trip and shall have to lay here for several
                        <lb n="009"/> days to have it mended or probably a
                        <lb n="010"/> new one made.  I cannot learn what our
